author: Lyzza
title: Lincoln Chafee Ends His Presidential Campaign
text: Posts: 1,524 Lincoln Chafee Ends His Presidential Campaign Looks like Chafee is also out now. Clearing up the Democratic choices a bit, I guess. Not that Chafee or Webb were really going to siphon a lot of caucus goers from Clinton and Sanders. It can hurt in the first round at a precinct, though, which can mess up your second round if suddenly supporters think they need to jump ship to be on the "winning" side. Caucuses can be a weird phenomenon! Crazy stuff. Anyway, so long Chafee! Thanks for playing.
